{"tid":1023180,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)龍出生天 新舊逃出魔幻記","createTime":"2019-02-15T14:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T19:30:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7de125784c5a408ca4dfaa6561e9c71f0ed8936","tid":1023180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:37:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=ce434722\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=587c0abb\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=35471126\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://img31.mtime.cn/mt/2014/02/22/231940.76432374_270X405X4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg31.mtime.cn%2Fmt%2F2014%2F02%2F22%2F231940.76432374_270X405X4.jpg&h=7049c8bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b6/Jumanji_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb6%2FJumanji_poster.jpg&h=8a2e6801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/1/13/Jumanji_Welcome_to_the_Jungle_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F1%2F13%2FJumanji_Welcome_to_the_Jungle_Poster.jpg&h=ff8703b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一場意外的大爆炸把連接紐約曼哈頓和新澤西州的主要隧道封閉，由於爆炸正值下班的交通巔峰期，隧道頓時哀嚎遍野。面臨這場災難的汽車族人人自危，驚惶失措，此時一名叫做奇德的前緊療急救服務中心主任挺身而出；在隧道隨時都可能崩塌之際，奇德以冷靜的頭腦和矯健的身手拯救罹難的人讓他們得以重見天日<br />\n<br />\n2.這是非一般的棋藝遊戲，驚險刺激而魅力所在是可以體驗前所未有的冒險，像是家中出現獅子、猴子、叢林裡各式各樣的生物，甚至是把玩家傳送到未知的非洲叢林。參與者的代價是遊戲開始便要走畢全程才能離開。<br />\n12歲的雅倫與莎拉在偶然機會下參與了這個亡命的遊戲棋玩意，怪事發生，雅倫被攝進魔幻世界中，突然人間蒸發。26年後，兩名小童茱迪與彼得搬到雅倫的舊居，意外地將雅倫在棋中世界釋放出來。同時棋裏的原始猛獸亦一併來到人類世界並進行破壞。拯救世界的方法便是找回莎拉，完成當年未下完的棋&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.1996年，新罕布希爾州布蘭福德鎮，少年亞歴克斯&middot;佛利克得到一個叫作《野蠻遊戲》之桌遊，其被他父親於海邊慢跑時從沙灘上撿回來。由於對桌遊不感興趣，亞歴克斯將遊戲盒丟在一旁後繼續玩電子遊戲；當他晚上睡覺時被一陣光芒驚醒後，再度打開遊戲盒後突然發現桌遊已經變成一個動作冒險類遊戲卡。感興趣的亞歴克斯將其插在自己的遊戲機上，剛開始玩不久就突然被吸入遊戲裏。2016年，二十年後，本地高中的四名學生被留校察看：幫別人代寫作業的史賓賽&middot;吉品、抄襲史賓賽作文的安東尼&middot;「冰箱」&middot;強森、考試途中打手機並自以為是的貝珊妮&middot;沃克、以及不想參與體育課並頂撞老師的瑪莎&middot;卡普利。四人被校長派到高中地下室清理舊文件時，剛好找到仍然插著野蠻遊戲卡的舊遊戲機，四人為打發時間而選好各自的角色後，突然間也被集體吸進遊戲裏<br />\n<br />\n10 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=2b920a2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=zBdjJXAkzC5SgMGJ5jx7qgZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9dab7093\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f3c0f77b14f967b6156ad609eefcb5619686a1","tid":1023180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27f954f51ff3b42f5803a09f5e7a4ca98d20f6c","tid":1023180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T15:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd0bdbed9815a2870b3e80a0823cac9b9bf856b","tid":1023180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19eb0f5df21bb71c1d282020e59dd6214e900cf","tid":1023180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T16:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc7a29065b67ca9103bb6ced8bc5f5ac5e37d36","tid":1023180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0299d2f7a994a5bb48b6a473a86ce47a6ce04ea","tid":1023180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T19:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73e0cb8910b5a05b7f206b953cc61e486201dbd","tid":1023180,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T19:30:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im